Justin NELSON, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0657 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 17, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:
